The document coverage calculation is on a per ({{arxiv_2111_13611_FO0114||FO}}, {{arxiv_2111_13611_FO0115||FO}}) pair basis. In a single iteration, all the proposed methods are given a set of documents partitioned by ({{arxiv_2111_13611_FO0116||FO}}, {{arxiv_2111_13611_FO0117||FO}}) pairs. Each method uses its technique to rank the documents, and the top {{arxiv_2111_13611_FO0118||FO}} ranked documents are given to the RE API (Rosette or Diffbot) for obtaining the set of relational tuples.